// Application icon. The rexglue window class loads it by the name "MAINICON"
// (LoadIconW(hinstance, L"MAINICON") in window_win.cpp) and applies it via
// WM_SETICON, so this is the icon for the .exe, the window title bar, and the
// taskbar. Windows Explorer shows it for the file too.
MAINICON ICON "Icon.ico"
